{"tid":170063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【求助】有冇巴絲打熟貨van依行？","createTime":"2017-03-24T13:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T14:17:59.000Z","uid":93279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0068c42ed7848e65d5c0a0b5477adf226ea9cced","tid":170063,"uid":93279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"事緣 父親之前做開裝修<br />\n大約由上年開始就冇乜工開<br />\n原本跟開嗰個老細投唔到標，所以冇工開<br />\n之後過大半年後 佢就決定分期供，買架貨van轉行啦<br />\n咁佢一路都係上call 台 等job咁<br />\n<br />\n但係原來我發現佢其實係call台，接唔到幾多轉車，可能加上新入行，冇乜舊客<br />\n<br />\n一日$500都未必夠<br />\n<br />\n仲要扣油錢，停車場錢，call 台錢<br />\n一個月計埋，連供車錢都未必夠<br />\n<br />\n我見佢愈翻愈頹咁 都唔知點幫佢<br />\n上網睇 gogovan, 個個都話垃圾<br />\n真心<br />\n<br />\n想問下巴絲 知唔知邊個台會比較多job接咁<br />\n或者有冇其他方法 起碼有少少穩定翻收入<br />\n真係好擔心父親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dea3b99e489253a245c1d3f2e9a5af13644b55f","tid":170063,"uid":93279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e43ed59143f0c6239a3bd94847e68a740ac50e3","tid":170063,"uid":93279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663fd2e8de649c8bad789036e91dd92063b6f31f","tid":170063,"uid":88853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"Call4van<br />\n想儲客就印卡片派啦"}]}